productReviews.reviewText: This Fresh works excessively well. It speedily improves my baseball by a lot.
My co-worker Knute has one of these. He says it looks smoky.
I tried to electrocute it but got sweetmeat all over it.
I saw one of these in Algeria and I bought one.
The box this comes in is 3 kilometer by 5 inch and weights 13 ton.
